headline: Goldman Sachs Rates ONEOK Inc. (OKE) a ‘Neutral’ Amid Acquisitions Boost
summary: ONEOK, Inc. (NYSE:OKE) is one of the most profitable energy stocks to buy right now. On September 30, Goldman Sachs resumed coverage of the stock with a ‘Neutral’ rating and a $75 price target. The coverage comes on the company expanding its footprint through acquisitions.
